node.text:
Introducing the Elevated Paisley collection. 

Suede uppers draped with a bold paisley print. Featured on the Accel OG and Evant in a tone on tone rendition in True Red and rich Black colorways. #eS_Paisley #eS_Evant

Available now at esskateboarding.com
